                     <interp inst="t18470816-1976-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing 1 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. Bank-note, the monies of <persName id="t18470816-name-1318" type="victimName">
