                        <interp inst="t18470816-name-1320" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE GOODE.</persName>
                  </hi> I took the prisoner on Friday evening at Mr. White<lb></lb>wood's—I told her she was charged with stealing a 5<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. note—I cautioned her that I should tell the Magistrate what she said—she was anxious to tell the truth, and said she had taken the note and burnt it, and had taken other things besides.</p>
